90028 = { #Hereward the Wake
	name = "Hereweard"
	dna = 90028_hereweard_the_wake
	dynasty = 2004006 #Probably not a descendant of Oslac, but we don't have any other leads
	martial = 11 #A gifted military commander
	diplomacy = 5 #...but not exactly a diplomat
	prowess = 10 #Capable duelist
	religion = "catholic"
	culture = anglo_norse
	father = 90031
	trait = education_martial_3
	trait = ambitious
	trait = vengeful #killed a bunch of Normans who killed his brother
	trait = wrathful #see above
	trait = forder #defended the fenlands
	trait = adventurer
	1044.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	1060.1.1 = {
		add_spouse = 90160 #Turfida
		add_pressed_claim = title:c_cambridgeshire
		give_nickname = nick_the_wake
		effect = {
			set_landless_government_effect = yes
			add_trait = lifestyle_blademaster #noted duelist
			add_trait_xp = {
				trait = lifestyle_blademaster
				value = {
					integer_range = {
						min = medium_lifestyle_random_xp_low
						max = medium_lifestyle_random_xp_high
					}
				}
			}
			add_trait = gallowsbait #exiled and outlawed
			add_trait_xp = {
				trait = gallowsbait
				track = bandit
				value = {
					integer_range = {
						min = medium_lifestyle_random_xp_low
						max = medium_lifestyle_random_xp_high
					}
				}
			}
			add_trait = the_wake
			add_character_flag = special_laamp_char
			add_character_flag = do_not_generate_starting_family
			if = {
				limit = { is_ruler = yes }
				create_maa_regiment = {
					type = huscarl
					size = 5
				}
				add_contact = character:364
				add_opinion = {
					target = character:364
					modifier = respect_opinion
					opinion = 50
				}
				reverse_add_opinion = {
					target = character:364
					modifier = respect_opinion
					opinion = 50
				}
				domicile ?= {
					add_domicile_building = camp_main_02
					add_domicile_building = supply_tent_01
					add_domicile_building = supply_tent_02
					add_domicile_building = supply_tent_smithy
					add_domicile_building = supply_tent_arsenal
					add_domicile_building = camp_fire_01
					add_domicile_building = camp_fire_02
					add_domicile_building = proving_grounds_01
					add_domicile_building = proving_grounds_02
					add_domicile_building = proving_grounds_personal_bouts
				}
			}
		}
	}
	1066.1.6 = {
		effect = {
			add_opinion = {
				target = character:122
				modifier = demanded_eviction_opinion
			}
		}
	}
	1094.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}

####################################### Dynasty: house_Plant #######################################
204500 = {
	name = "Henry" #Henry II
	dynasty_house = house_Plant
	dna = 204500_henry_II_plantagenet
	diplomacy = 7
	martial = 8
	stewardship = 8
	intrigue = 8
	learning = 7
	prowess = 0 #More a strategist than a fighter: we have to keep the base apocalyptically low because otherwise he's go so many joint prowess-martial mods that he become a godly duellist.
	religion = "catholic"
	culture = "english"

norman_crispin_06 = {
	name = Robert #Robert Crispin 'Phrangopoulos'
	dna = norman_crispin_06_robert_phrangopoulos
	dynasty = norman_crispin #Crispin
	culture = norman
	religion = catholic
	father = norman_crispin_01
	trait = education_martial_3
	trait = brave
	trait = wrathful
	trait = greedy
	trait = reaver
	trait = lifestyle_traveler
	trait = aggressive_attacker
	disallow_random_traits = yes
	1040.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	1066.1.1 = {
		effect = {
			set_relation_best_friend = { reason = friend_generic_history target = character:34220 } #Roussel de Bailleul
			give_nickname = nick_phrangopoulos
			add_trait_xp = {
				trait = lifestyle_traveler
				track = travel
				value = { 45 55 }
			}
			add_trait_xp = {
				trait = lifestyle_traveler
				track = danger
				value = { 25 35 }
			}
			if = {
				limit = {
					has_dlc_feature = roads_to_power
				}
				change_government = landless_adventurer_government
				create_maa_regiment = {
					type = conrois
					size = 3
				}
			}
			add_character_flag = special_laamp_char
			add_character_flag = do_not_generate_starting_family
		}
	}
	1073.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}
